{
  "stem": "10283.4",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "For operator, we would call it here, in the blouse factory in Bern, and would I want to go to Bern and work there on a power machine?",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I said, yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So when Werner heard that, he put in the only way he could get out of the camp was being a dishwasher.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he-- they were short on those labor-intensive things.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he put in for dishwasher, and within one week, he was in Bern, washing dishes.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was still in the camp because my liberation took a little longer.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But we finally got together.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he had to live on top in the-- in the attic with other dishwashers, other crooks.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was very primitive, and very amazing to us how unsanitary and primitive the conditions were in a first-class-- so-called first-class restaurant in Bern.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But he made it through.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I had that job in the blouse factory.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then we decided to get married.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And through different circumstances, too.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we-- my mother gave her consent.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And on the 1st of May in 1945, we got married in Bern.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And in the same newspaper that our, you know, the little notice appeared that we got married.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The headline of that newspaper was, 'Hitler is Dead and the War is Almost Over.' And that was a very memorable day.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I still have that newspaper too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we got married.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And, you know, we-- we lived in Bern then.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And my mother was free in Bern too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "She wanted to be near me, so she took a job as a maid in a Swiss household.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And so we lived in Bern for awhile.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
